headline: 1 Stock-Split Stock to Buy Hand Over Fist in July and 1 to Avoid
summary: Stock splits don't change fundamentals, but there's some evidence they can lead to outperformance.  O'Reilly has been a longtime winner in the auto parts industry.  Interactive Brokers has delivered strong growth, but lower interest rates would put a significant dent in its profits.
